data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
After clicking OK, you will see your new Authenticator with the Authenticator Code shown in the center window and the Serial Number near the bottom.
If the Code is not visible, click the button to the left to refresh it.
You can right-click anwhere within the window to bring up the menu.
Remember you must keep the authenticator data file private and safe.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Your Authenticator has been successfully registered with Battle.net.
You will need to login to your account and add a new Battle.net Mobile Authenticator to your account.
You will be asked for a Serial Number and the Authenticator Code.
